cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE

The paper involves the use of deep learning for image reconstruction in cardiovascular MR, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of residual convolutional neural networks also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The acquisition of real-time data and comparison to Compressed Sensing (CS) suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) and neural engineering (cs.NE) sub-categories.
